  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "In addition, as was a cross-current of cultures, as I mentioned before, from one side, if you go out in Vilna, you could see a beautiful cathedral with-- in the center of the city, built on the-- on the-- due to the influence of the Italian Renaissance and built by the Polish szlachta.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will come to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The second one [? we ?] [? saw ?] the other cultures.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And normally, we see the Gothic and the big-- the big cross-section and the-- and the [? church is ?] [?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "St. ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Anne. ?] In addition, we saw the influence of the Russian-- Russian culture, the Byzantine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we see over there the-- the St.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Peters church.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Jewish-- the Jewish shuls were not-- you couldn't see them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because most of them were underground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And according to the law of the land, they had to be built lower than the churches and not to have-- not to expose themself.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were built mostly as-- as over houses or were located over houses or underground.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The most famous of them was the-- the Great Shul.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Great Shul was where it was located is second ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a shul of the Gaon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gaon of Vilna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Talmud. ?] And the thing is it was about five flights underneath.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The center, it was built still was a replica of the [NON-ENGLISH], of the temple.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it's considered one of the most beautiful structures in Europe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the middle, it was a bema.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And it's had the same-- it's has same pedestals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it had the same-- the-- it's had the different-- different architecture-- the Corinthian-- a mixture of Corinthian and architecture imported from the Italian-- Italy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But in addition, it's had some facades all around.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
